subject: Bathing Suits
Swimming
lead_paragraph: The uncertainty over high-tech swimsuits is likely to extend into the world championships in July. Cornel Marculescu, FINA’s executive director, said this year was a “transition period” before tougher suit regulations are created for 2010.
